                    <h6 class="section-title bg-white text-start text-primary pe-3 mt-4 mt-lg-0">Estate Planning</h6>
                    <div class="section-title-line"></div>
                    <p>Estate planning is the process of arranging for the management and distribution of your assets after your death. It is a critical aspect of financial planning, particularly for individuals with substantial wealth. At Ratnesh Wealth Partners, we offer comprehensive estate planning services to ensure that your assets are transferred according to your wishes and in a tax-efficient manner.</p>
                    <p class="mb-4">Our team helps you develop an estate plan that addresses your unique needs, including the creation of wills, trusts, powers of attorney, and other legal documents. We also offer strategies to minimize estate taxes and ensure that your loved ones are financially secure. Estate planning is not just about distributing assets; it’s about creating a legacy that reflects your values and wishes.</p>
                    <p class="mb-4">At Ratnesh Wealth Partners, we collaborate with legal and tax professionals to create a comprehensive estate plan that provides clarity and peace of mind for you and your family. Our advisors will help you navigate complex estate planning issues, such as charitable giving, family wealth transfers, and succession planning, ensuring that your wealth is protected, and your legacy endures.</p>
